Usage: deletePartition [-help] [-undo_tcl_file <string>] { <ptnName>  | -all   | -nested  | -non_leaf  }

-help                       # Prints out the command usage
<ptnName>                   # Specifies the name of the partition.
                            # (string, optional)
-all                        # Specifies all partition. (bool, optional)
-nested                     # Delete all nested partititons in the design. 
                            # (bool, optional)
-non_leaf                   # Delete all Non-leaf partitions in the design.
                            # (bool, optional)
-undo_tcl_file <string>     # Specifies file which can be sourced to undo
                            # deletion of partitions (string, optional)